b'The Office for Advising Development'
b''
b'Welcome! The UIC Office For Advising Development supports undergraduate academic advising at UIC.'
b'Advising at UIC is guided by its mission statement:'
b'The mission of academic advising at the University of Illinois at Chicago is to ensure successful undergraduate educational experiences. Academic advising is centered in the colleges. The larger advising network assists students with making the transition to college life and guides their informed decisions about the academic priorities, progress, and goals integral to completing degrees and preparing for careers.'
b'The Office For Advising Development is committed to ensuring that\xc2\xa0students and advisors have an optimum advising experience in this cooperative endeavor. The\xc2\xa0center provides information about advising services, provides professional development for advisors, administers programs to help advisors and students evaluate performance in select courses each semester, and helps students find their advisors.'
b'Do you have a question related to advising? Ask us!'
b'Ask us!'
b'Need information about UIC resources? Check out ASK UIC!'
